languages.text: "Мы ощущаем большое свершение, яркий отпечаток в сущем. Ты сделал{mf||а} что-то очень важное. Что?"
"We sense that a great deed has been done, a vivid imprint on existence. You did something very important. What was it?"

languages.text: 「偉大な行いがなされたことを感じています。存在に鮮やかな印を刻みました。あなたは何か重要なことをした。それは何だったのか？」
languages.original_text: "We sense that a great deed has been done, a vivid imprint on existence. You did something very important. What was it?"

traits.locale_text: 「偉大な行いがなされたことを感じています。存在に鮮やかな印を刻みました。あなたは何か重要なことをした。それは何だったのか？」

languages.text: “我们感觉到发生了一件壮举，于存在上留下了生动的印记。你做了一件非常重要的事，发生了什么？”
languages.original_text: "We sense that a great deed has been done, a vivid imprint on existence. You did something very important. What was it?"

traits.locale_text: “我们感觉到发生了一件壮举，于存在上留下了生动的印记。你做了一件非常重要的事，发生了什么？”

languages.text: "Wir spüren, dass eine große Tat vollbracht wurde, der Existenz ein lebhafter Stempel aufgedrückt wurde. Ihr habt etwas sehr Wichtiges getan. Was war es?"
languages.original_text: "We sense that a great deed has been done, a vivid imprint on existence. You did something very important. What was it?"

traits.locale_text: "Wir spüren, dass eine große Tat vollbracht wurde, der Existenz ein lebhafter Stempel aufgedrückt wurde. Ihr habt etwas sehr Wichtiges getan. Was war es?"

languages.text: « Nous sentons que vous avez accompli quelque chose de très important, que vous avez marqué l'existence de votre empreinte. Qu'avez-vous fait ? »
languages.original_text: "We sense that a great deed has been done, a vivid imprint on existence. You did something very important. What was it?"

traits.locale_text: « Nous sentons que vous avez accompli quelque chose de très important, que vous avez marqué l'existence de votre empreinte. Qu'avez-vous fait ? »

languages.text: «Percibimos que se ha realizado una gran hazaña que ha dejado una vívida impronta en la existencia. Ha hecho usted algo muy importante. ¿Qué ha sido?».
languages.original_text: "We sense that a great deed has been done, a vivid imprint on existence. You did something very important. What was it?"

traits.locale_text: «Percibimos que se ha realizado una gran hazaña que ha dejado una vívida impronta en la existencia. Ha hecho usted algo muy importante. ¿Qué ha sido?».

languages.text: "Varoluşta canlı bir iz bırakan, büyük bir icraat seziyoruz. Çok önemli bir şey yaptınız... Ne yaptınız?"
languages.original_text: "We sense that a great deed has been done, a vivid imprint on existence. You did something very important. What was it?"

traits.locale_text: "Büyük bir icraat yapıldığını seziyoruz, varoluşta canlı bir iz bıraktı. Çok önemli bir şey yaptınız... Peki, yaptığınız şey neydi?"
